Erausq Tekram~
   There is an image of a warped, five-pointed compass embedded
in the broken cobblestones of the square.  A short squat fountain
belches forth brown, bile-like goop that cannot possibly be healthy
to drink.  Somehow it's clear, this is the epicenter of this strange
withered land of Draagdim.
   To the east and west a jagged road leads through the forsaken
town.  To the north and south, more abandoned squares like this
one.
